"Verbindungsabbrüchen dauerhaft."
msgstr ""
"The login process must always be initiated by the client. In case of "
"connection interruptions, the client must re-establish the connection "
"automatically. Ensure that the client has an auto-connect function. "
"Otherwise, you will permanently lose the data connection in case of "
"interruptions."

