"Lichtverhältnisse anpassen. So können Sie nachts das Display ohne "
"Sichteinschränkungen ablesen."
msgstr ""
"For longer night drives, a red backlight is recommended, set to a moderate "
"brightness of, for example, 50%. With red light, the eye doesn't have to "
"constantly adjust to changing light conditions. This allows you to read the "
"display at night without any visual impairment."

#: ../../usermanual/configuration.rst:828 5fdba9af508e4b8d802ac7f384c66ac3
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Je höher die Helligkeit der Hintergrundbeleuchtung eingestellt wird, um so "
