"consumed. White backlighting consumes the most power, as all three colors of"
" the RGB LED are used to generate white light. Pure primary colors like red,"
" green, and blue consume the least power. With mixed colors, the RGB LEDs "
"are driven at different intensities, resulting in higher power consumption "
"than with the primary colors. Here are two examples:"

